      <title>大众汽车将投资27亿美元在中国生产基地</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-invest-27-billion-chinese-production-site-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车周四宣布，计划在中国投资 25 亿欧元（26.8 亿美元），扩大其位于安徽省合肥市的生产和创新中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-invest-27-billion-chinese-production-site-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 11:35:03 GMT</pubDate>
